WEBVTT

00:00:01.380 --> 00:00:04.618
I'd like you to imagine,
just for a moment,

00:00:04.642 --> 00:00:09.696
that your eyelashes grew inwards
instead of outwards,

00:00:09.720 --> 00:00:12.021
so that every time you blinked,

00:00:12.045 --> 00:00:15.141
they would scrape
the front of your eyeballs,

00:00:15.165 --> 00:00:16.942
damaging the corneas,

00:00:16.966 --> 00:00:20.686
so that slowly and painfully,
you went blind.

00:00:21.307 --> 00:00:25.117
Well, that's what happens
to a person who has trachoma.

00:00:25.607 --> 00:00:30.776
Now, this little boy here, Pamelo,
from Zambia, he has trachoma.